{"tid":1564812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【用完即棄】努欽稱香港示威活動不是美中貿易談判一部分","createTime":"2019-09-13T02:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T05:38:47.000Z","uid":156363,"like":8,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"686969ef929c4f759dc227366e2381483752584b","tid":1564812,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:10:04.000Z","msg":"美國財長努欽說，下月初在華盛頓舉行的美中新一輪高級別經貿磋商之前，在本月先舉行的較低級別會晤，美方希望取得進展，又說香港的示威活動，不是談判的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n努欽又說，總統特朗普準備在貿易談判中，保持甚至提高對進口美國的中國商品徵收的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n彭博早前報道，特朗普一些高級貿易顧問，最近幾日討論與中方達成一份臨時協議的可能性，協議將首次提出，推遲甚至取消美國部分關稅措施，換取中方在知識產權及農產品採購方面的承諾，雙方代表將在華盛頓會面時討論。<br />\n<br />\n不過美國全國廣播公司商業頻道，引述白宮一名高級官員報道，美方「絕不可能」與中方達成一份這樣的臨時協議。"},{"pid":"a8e6faa64ba4cb81d847ba1931e8e2d93a1fe6ce","tid":1564812,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"510b1311fb3b00cd1177a7fc012e798d7a532fea","tid":1564812,"uid":22360,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:11:33.000Z","msg":"心水清就得，都係做番自己野"},{"pid":"c999e6ef7bc265fbb468a9040d3cdf7e2ac64342","tid":1564812,"uid":144626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"Mnuchink<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/d